766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of the Paris Games, athletes were concerned with theshallow water depthat La Defense Arena and the potential \\\"slowness\\\" of the pool.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"theshallow water\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"depthat La Defense Arena\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential \\\"slowness\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 898}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At just 2.15 meters deep, about seven and a half feet, the Paris pool was 31.5 inches shallower than the Tokyo venue in 2021.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 973, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999951837708, \"rank\": 4.816255992611382e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1019, \"end\": 1024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997312684255506, \"rank\": 0.0002686893777814578, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Psychologically, swimmers believe depth affects how \\\"fast\\\" a pool feels andscienceactually backs that so-called superstition as fact.\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"depth\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"a pool\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"that so-called superstition\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The deeper a pool is, the \\\"faster\\\" it can be due to less water volume for waves to reflect off the bottom and cause surface turbulence in.\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pool\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"less water volume\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"surface turbulence\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kyle Sockwell, a former Bob Bowmanswimmer at Arizona Stateand now a popular social media commentator on the sport, posted his in-person observations about the \\\"wavy\\\" pool and how it may have impacted swimmers' times.\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Broflovski\", \"score\": 0.993696387683756, \"rank\": 0.006198888683963384, \"text\": \"Kyle\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Broflovski\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Broflovski\"}, {\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Casale\", \"score\": 0.5462307829922114, \"rank\": 0.5999140119737586, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Casale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Casale\"}, {\"begin\": 1361, \"end\": 1368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\", \"score\": 0.9591655110617568, \"rank\": 0.021882000111342115, \"text\": \"Arizona\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"now a popular social media commentator\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"person\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"wavy\\\" pool\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers' times\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not sure how well it comes through on camera but this pool is WAVY and stays wavy for a long time.Athletes are undoubtedly swimming through some chop on second 50s and beyond and it's likely (in my opinion) impacting a resistance heavy stroke like breaststroke more than others.\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"camera\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"this pool\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"some chop\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1683}, {\"ngram\": \"second 50s\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"my opinion\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1739}, {\"ngram\": \"a resistance heavy stroke\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, former Australian swimmer and Olympic medalistJames Magnussen instead laid the blameat the feet of Paris organizers and the conditions at the athletes' village, writing on July 30 \\\"This Olympics is showing that it may be one of the toughest environments we have seen to produce world record swims.\\\"\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1830, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9613957955103829, \"rank\": 0.038750935845967394, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1922, \"end\": 1927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999951837708, \"rank\": 4.816255992611382e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic medalistJames Magnussen\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"the blameat\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"the feet\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"the conditions\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1957}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"This Olympics\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"the toughest environments\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"world record swims\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He went on to claim that \\\"the lack of world records boils down to this whole eco-friendly, carbon footprint, vegan-first mentality [at the Olympic Village] rather than [prioritizing] high performance.\\\"\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"world records\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2174}, {\"ngram\": \"this whole eco-friendly, carbon footprint\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2277}, {\"ngram\": \"high performance\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Magnussen's assertions are much harder to prove and, regardless of theOlympic Village's viral unpopularity, are quite far-fetched.\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2456, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Magnussen's assertions\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Village's viral unpopularity\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in the case of a shallow pool, organizers can not necessarily be blamed.\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"a shallow pool\", \"from\": 2477,